comment: /**  * Sends an http response to the channel. The listener will be executed once the send process has been  * completed.  *  * @param response to send to channel  * @param listener to execute upon send completion  */
code: /**  * Sends an http response to the channel. The listener will be executed once the send process has been  * completed.  *  * @param response to send to channel  * @param listener to execute upon send completion  */ void sendResponse(HttpResponse response, ActionListener<Void> listener).

comment: /**  * Returns the local address for this channel.  *  * @return the local address of this channel.  */
code: /**  * Returns the local address for this channel.  *  * @return the local address of this channel.  */ InetSocketAddress getLocalAddress().

comment: /**  * Returns the remote address for this channel. Can be null if channel does not have a remote address.  *  * @return the remote address of this channel.  */
code: /**  * Returns the remote address for this channel. Can be null if channel does not have a remote address.  *  * @return the remote address of this channel.  */ InetSocketAddress getRemoteAddress().
